data.text: @br00klynb0und This was a shit week for me,  and watching her reign like a goddamn queen in TLJ serves as a potent reminder of hope and sacrifice in the face of utter desolation. The tears we shed are lubricant for all the feels.
@br00klynb0und Every shot of her in that movie is perfection, partially because it allows me to cry my eyes out of my head.
